comments.body:
I don't think the team has any time to implement this at the moment, but I don't think we'd object to a PR adding support for it.

I do have some concerns about the user interface for such a system; how does one specify which layers to include/exclude, and how do we provide a sensible error message if someone tries to import the image on a system that does not have those missing layers? These seem solvable, but I want to make sure that we produce a good experience for users.

@mtrmac PTAL
